      "content": "But you said they're \"essential\" and a \"proven method.\" Doesn't that ignore a lot of the data from places like the US where crime is high even with certain laws? And how can you say they're \"proven\" when people argue the Second Amendment is an absolute right that can't be restricted like that? It feels like you're picking a side.",
